15_nenga_sakurai.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga_sakurai-thumb-500x750-8284.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br>樱井玲香<br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/12/16/141215_nenga_shiraishi.jpg\"><img alt=\"141215_nenga_shiraishi.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga_shiraishi-thumb-500x750-8286.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br>白石麻衣<br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/12/16/141215_nenga_nishino.jpg\"><img alt=\"141215_nenga_nishino.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga_nishino-thumb-500x750-8288.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br>西野七濑<br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/12/16/141215_nenga_hashimoto.jpg\"><img alt=\"141215_nenga_hashimoto.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga_hashimoto-thumb-500x750-8290.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br>桥本奈奈未<br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/12/16/141215_nenga_hoshino.jpg\"><img alt=\"141215_nenga_hoshino.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga_hoshino-thumb-500x750-8292.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br>星野南<br><br>「盘旋AR贺年片」是指在App Store、谷歌Play上发布的“SONPAR AR”的应用软件下载到智能手机中，然后把收到的贺年卡的受欢迎（收件人姓名版）放在一起，成员们用各种各样的姿势表现了新年的360°AR照片可以享受的服务。BGM将使用于2015年1月7日发售的第一张专辑《透明的颜色》中收录的《革命之马》、《自由的彼方》，敬请期待！<br><br></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.62;\">详细的请看蛋糕。<br><a href=\"http://guruguru-ar-nenga.jp\">http://guruguru-ar-nenga.jp</a><br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/12/16/141215_nenga3.jpg\"><img alt=\"141215_nenga3.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/12/141215_nenga3-thumb-500xauto-8294.jpg\" width=\"500\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a><br><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014